Package: ggmlR
Type: Package
Title: Machine Learning Tensor Operations via ggml with Vulkan Backend
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-01-10
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Yuri", "Baramykov",
      email = "lbsbmsu@mail.ru",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: R interface to ggml library for GPU-accelerated tensor 
    operations and machine learning inference. Supports Vulkan compute 
    for AMD, Intel, and NVIDIA GPUs. Includes quantization (4-bit, 8-bit) 
    and optimized kernels for LLM inference.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
SystemRequirements: Vulkan headers and loader (libvulkan-dev), Mesa RADV drivers for AMD GPU

